These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, japanese, thai
1. the thai is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the thai is between the indian and the japanese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | indian | thai | japanese |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, sports
1. the person watching disaster movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching sports movies##2
2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | disaster | horror |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, folk, metal
1. the fan of folk is between the fan of ambient and the fan of metal##2
2. the fan of folk is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | metal | folk | ambient |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: ferret, guinea-pig, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
2. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | ferret | snake | guinea-pig |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, milk
1. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking milk and the person drinking juice##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | juice | cola | milk |

 #################################
 
