.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-7::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, hedgehog
1. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the frog##2
2. the owner of the cat is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |  2  |  3   |
| Pet   | hedgehog | cat | frog |

